# Security

See [docs/SECURITY.md](../../docs/SECURITY.md) for full detail.

- **OWASP Top 10**: Mitigate injection, broken auth, XSS, etc.
- **Defense in depth**: Validate at every layer (API, app, data).
- **No secrets in code**: Use env vars or secrets manager.
- **Input validation**: Validate/sanitise at boundaries (e.g. Zod for request bodies).
- **Auth/authz**: Check permissions in application layer.
